title: ISic000122. I.Sicily inscription 000122
body:
Facsimile Images

Aelia ((·))
Alce
v(ixit) ((·)) a(nnis) ((·)) XI[.]

Apparatus criticus

Text from autopsy; Bivona: XI; in theory there is room in the lacuna at the end of the line for one more character, but almost certainly not more, so XII is also possible.

English translation

Aelia Alce lived eleven(?) years.

commentary
